export interface IUser{
    id: number,
    role: string,
    name: string,
    lastName: string,
    quote: string,
    birthday: string,
    nativeCity: string,
    email: string, 
    status: string,
    freinds: any
}

export class User implements IUser{
    id = -1
    role = "null"
    name = "null"
    lastName = "null"
    quote = "null"
    birthday = "null"
    nativeCity = "null"
    email = "null"
    status = "null"
    freinds: any
}
